title: Gamma Ray - Skeletons & Majesties Live - 2012 (DVDRip)
description:
Skeletons & Majesties Live is a live recording of the band's performance at the legendary Z7 in Pratteln, Switzerland on April 29th, 2011. 

Gamma Ray have long been considered a metal band full of surprises which may be one of the reasons why their fan base continues to flourish. Spring 2011 saw the four musicians embark on a club tour through Germany and Switzerland, expanding on the concept of their exceptional EP Skeletons & Majesties (new versions of songs which didn't receive the attention they deserve, as well as unplugged versions of some of our classics) on stage. The band's aficionados know that Gamma Ray is guaranteed to deliver yet another full frontal assault on the senses.
